title: California Girls: Karaoke Intervals
description:
Two spirited cyclists get carried away when they find an unusual and happy way to cheat their workout. Follow the harebrained adventures of Jackie Wolfe and Chrissy Crane in this very Californian comedy. 

Created, Written & Directed by Erin Lamb & Jennifer Whalen
Produced by Jennifer Whalen
Director of Photography: Chris G. Cleary
Cinematography by Chris G. Cleary & John Geronilla
Editing by D.C. Irvin
Audio Operator: Lisa Corral
Titles by Joshua M. Paulin

CAST
Jennifer Whalen as Jackie Wolfe
Erin Lamb as Chrissy Crane
Phil Gaimon as himself
Jesse Anthony as himself
Zach Sellers as Karaoke MC
Stefano Barberi as himself
